{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回 何处不相逢\n\n李寻欢在冷香小筑外遭遇藏剑山庄少庄主游龙生的偷袭，以飞刀化解危机。龙啸云出面调停，介绍游龙生乃当代第一剑客天山雪鹰子的传人。\"铁面无私\"赵正义闻讯赶来质问李寻欢杀死丘独之事，李寻欢坦言杀人是被迫自卫，赵正义虽愤怒却无可奈何。\n\n龙啸云与李寻欢在冷香小筑叙旧，回忆十年前李寻欢与林诗音的往事。李寻欢触景生情，感叹物是人非。龙啸云透露林仙儿一直保持冷香小筑原样不动，暗示其对李寻欢的执念。\n\n林仙儿登场，以天下第一美人的姿态与李寻欢展开心理交锋。她声称自己从未让其他男人进入冷香小筑，只为保留李寻欢的气息。林仙儿坦白她追求金丝甲是为了亲手杀死梅花盗，从而不必嫁人。她提议让李寻欢以金丝甲为诱饵，在冷香小筑设下圈套对付梅花盗。两人在试探与调情中达成协议，林仙儿展露出高超的诱惑手段，而李寻欢则保持着冷静与警觉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有趣有趣，阁下的确有趣得很，貂裘上居然还长着眼睛！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这件貂裘上若是没有长着眼睛，又怎会看见阁下的宝剑，又怎会躲得过阁下自背后刺来的一剑呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位都在说笑，'藏剑山庄'的少庄主，固然绝不会在乎区区一柄剑，但兄弟你又怎会在乎区区一袭貂裘呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位原来就是游少庄主！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，游兄不但是藏龙老人的公子，也是当代第一剑客'天山雪鹰子'前辈的惟一传人，两位正是一时之瑜亮，此后一定要多亲近亲近。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "亲近倒不敢，只不过这位朋友高姓大名？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "游兄原来还不认得我这位兄弟，他姓李，叫李寻欢，放眼当今天下，只怕也惟有我这兄弟够资格和游兄你交朋友了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然又是位名家子弟！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "外面那人是谁杀死的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了我还有谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你，我早该想到是你，你无论走到哪里，都会带来一片血腥气。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人不该杀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜他不是梅花盗。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然知道他不是梅花盗，为何还要下毒手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽也不想杀他，但也不愿被他杀了，无论如何，杀人总比被人杀好些。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他先要杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "平白无故，他为何要杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也觉得很奇怪，正想问问他，只可惜他不理我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何不留下他的活口？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也很想留下他的活口，只可惜我手里这柄刀一发出去，对方是活是死，就连我自己也无法控制了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既已出关，为何偏偏还要回来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因我对赵大爷想念得很，忍不住想回来瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好好好，这是你的好兄弟惹下来的祸，别人可管不着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有话好说，大哥何必发这么大的脾气？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有什么好说的！我们对付一个梅花盗，已经够头疼的了，如今再加上个'青魔'伊哭，谁还受得了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我杀了伊哭的爱徒丘独，伊哭知道了一定会来寻仇，但他要找的也只不过是我一个人而已，赵大爷你又何必替我担心呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丘独三更半夜到这里来，显然也没有存着什么好心，兄弟你杀他本就杀得没错，他若被我撞见，我只怕也要杀死他的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赵大爷毕竟老了，脾气越来越大，胆子却越来越小，其实伊哭来了又有何妨，在下也正好见识见识名满天下的探花飞刀！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "其实阁下若有此心，就并不一定要等伊哭来了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "兄弟，你这又是何苦？就算你瞧不起他们，不愿和他们交朋友，也不必得罪他们呀！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "他们反正早已认为我是不可救药了，我得不得罪他们都一样，倒不如索性将他气走，反而可以落得个眼前干净。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "朋友多一个总比少一个好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但世上又有几人能不负这'朋友'二字？像大哥你这样的朋友，无论谁只要交到一个已足够了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，兄弟，只要能听到你这句话，我就算将别的朋友全都得罪了，也是值得的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这些年来，你的咳嗽……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥，我现在只想见一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "是不是林仙儿？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥真不愧为我的知己。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我早就知道你迟早忍不住要想见她的，李寻欢若连天下第一美人都不想见，那么李寻欢就不是李寻欢了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你若想到这里来找她，却找错地方了，自从前天晚上的事发生了之后，她晚上已不敢再留在冷香小筑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这两天晚上，她一直陪着诗音在一起，你也正好顺便去看看诗音……唉，她究竟是个女人，你就算去安慰安慰她又有何妨？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "其实，她也不是不知道云儿的可恶，绝不会真的怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但我们既已来到这里，不如还是到冷香小筑去瞧瞧吧，说不定那林姑娘现在已回来了呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也好，看来你今天晚上若见不到她，只怕连觉都睡不着了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十年了……也许已不止十年了，有时'时间'仿佛过得很慢，但等它真过去时，你才会发现它快得令你吃惊。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你还记不记得我第一天到这里来的时候，那天好像也在下雪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我……我怎会忘记？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我记得那天我们两人几乎将你家的藏酒都喝光了，也是我惟一看到你喝醉的一次，但你却硬是不肯承认喝醉，还要和我打赌，说你可以用正楷将杜工部的'秋兴八首'写出来，而且绝对一笔不苟。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我也记得那次打赌还是我赢了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你大概未想到，过了十多年后，这枝笔还会在这里吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "笔虽然仍在，怎奈已换了主人……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "说来也奇怪，林仙儿好像早已算准你要回来似的，虽已住到这里好多年了，但这里的一草一木她都未动过……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "她本不必如此做的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我们并没有要她这么做，但她却说……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在这里，什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我……我还想在这里看看，不知道可不可以？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "当然可以，这本是你的地方，就算林仙儿回来，也只有欢迎的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "谁说你老了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你为什么闭上眼睛，难道不愿意见我么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我只不过是在回想那天你脱光了衣服时的模样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我本来希望你认不出我的，可是我也知道这希望并不大。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我若这么快就将你忘记了，你岂非也会觉得很失望？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可是你见到我并不吃惊，难道你早已想到我是谁了吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这也许是因为武林中能被称为'美人'的人并不多吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这也许是因为你见到伊哭的徒弟，就想到了我那双青魔手，见到了游龙生，就想到了我的鱼藏剑，是吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我只奇怪，你既然知道我在这里，怎么还敢来见我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "丑媳妇既然难免见公婆，躲着也没有用的，所以，龙四哥一叫我来，我立刻就赶着来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？是他要你来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你难道还不懂他的意思？他早就想为我们拉拢了，这也许是因为他觉得有些对不起你，抢了你的……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他并没有对不起我，任何人都没有对不起我，只有我对不起别人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你对不起谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我对不起的人太多了，连我自己都数不清。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "随便你怎么说，我都知道你绝不是这样的人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你知道我是怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我当然知道，我很小很小的时候，就听说过你的事了，所以当我知道这就是你以前住的地方时，我兴奋得简直没法子睡觉。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你看，这屋子里所有的东西，是不是全都和你十年前离开这里时一样？就连你藏在书架里的那瓶酒，我都没有动过，你可知道这是为了什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你当然不会知道，但我却可以告诉你，因为只有这样，我才能感觉到这是你住的地方，有时我甚至觉得你还在这屋子里，坐在这椅子上，静静地看着我，轻轻地陪着我说话。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有时我半夜醒来，总觉得你仿佛就睡在我身旁，那床上、枕头上，还留着你的气息！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "除了我之外，只怕还有别的人吧？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你以为这屋子还有别人进来过？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这地方已经属于你，你让谁进来都无妨。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你以为游龙生、丘独这些人一定进来过，是吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "告诉你，我从来也没有让他们走进过这道门，所以他们只有等在梅林中，我若肯让他们进来，丘独和秦重也许就不会死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "既是如此，你为何不让他们进来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只因为这是你的地方，我要……要替你保留着，绝不能让别的男人进来，破坏你留下来的……的……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "味道？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我的意思，你明白了么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但我却直到现在才知道我身上是有味道的……是什么味道？是香？还是臭？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我对你说了这些话，并不是为了要你耻笑我的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我的意思你还不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "如此说来，用不着别人拉拢，我也很有希望了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "若不是我早已……早已对你……那天我怎么会对你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "原来你那天只是为了喜欢我而那样做的，我还当你是为了金丝甲哩。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我……我当然也是为了金丝甲，但对象若不是你，我怎么肯……怎么肯……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "原来你那样做是一举两得。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你一定还在奇怪，我为什么那么想要金丝甲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我实在有点奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那只因我想亲手杀死梅花盗！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你总该知道，无论谁杀死梅花盗，我都要嫁给他，这活虽是我自己说的，可是其中也有很多苦衷。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你要亲手杀死梅花盗难道是为了要你自己嫁给你自己么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我这样做，只是为了我不愿嫁人，所以我若自己杀死梅花盗，就用不着嫁给别人了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只因天下的男人，没有一个是我看得上眼的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你自然是例外。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为你和别的男人都不同，那些人就像狗一样，无论我怎样对他们，他们还是要死缠着我，只有你……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "那么你为何不将金丝甲留在我这里，等我杀死了梅花盗，你再嫁给我，这样岂非也一举两得么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这实在是好主意，我为何没有想起来？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这么好的主意，除了我之外，还有淮能想得出？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道梅花盗这两天一定会来的，明天我就在这里等着他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你要我明天也到这里来，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你以我为饵，将他引来，反正金丝甲在你身上，你纵然制不住他，他无论如何也伤不了你的，你若制住了他……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好，明夜我一定来，我若不来，就是呆子了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你总算已学乖了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我本来就很乖。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你总算已学会让男人来主动。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你……你现在不会的……是吗？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你怎知道我不会？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为你是个君子，是吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我平生只做过一次君子，那次我后悔了三天。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "原来你不止学会了让男人主动，还学会了逃。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这全是你教我的，是你教我该如何勾引你，是吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    }
